Package: MLfused
Title: Multinomial Logistic Regression with Empirical-Likelihood Data Fusion
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits multinomial logistic regression models that incorporate
    external machine learning predictions via empirical-likelihood (EL)
    constraints. Implements Newton-step optimization with analytic gradient
    and Hessian, multiple sandwich-based standard error estimators (score-based,
    Theorem 3, bootstrap), and vectorized computation.
